rows.label: qst200231_0010
rows.name: Impressive, Glen.

rows.label: qst200231_0020
rows.name: Huh?!

rows.label: qst200231_0030
rows.name: You have done better than anyone could have hoped.

rows.label: qst200231_0040
rows.name: But... You get it now, don't you?

rows.label: qst200231_0050
rows.name: Just look at all this...

rows.label: qst200231_0060
rows.name:
All of it, come to pass because
of that girl.

rows.label: qst200231_0070
rows.name:
She needed money to save
her sick mother.

rows.label: qst200231_0080
rows.name:
She chose to do it through the thing that
she loved most: dancing.

rows.label: qst200231_0090
rows.name:
What I'm saying is,
she did the right thing for the right reasons.

rows.label: qst200231_0100
rows.name: But greed was her undoing...

rows.label: qst200231_0110
rows.name:
Enticed by a way to make even more money...
She caused this.

rows.label: qst200231_0120
rows.name:
The justice you believe in so strongly...crumbles so
very easily when faced with simple human desires.

rows.label: qst200231_0130
rows.name:
People can do terrible things
in the name of justice!

rows.label: qst200231_0140
rows.name: Ohhh... Put a sock in it, will ya?

rows.label: qst200231_0150
rows.name:
Do you think I'm an idiot?
Give me a break.

rows.label: qst200231_0160
rows.name:
Blaming all of this on the poor girl?
Telling me there ain't no justice?

rows.label: qst200231_0170
rows.name: You are the deluded one.

rows.label: qst200231_0180
rows.name: All of this is your fault, and yours alone!

rows.label: qst200231_0190
rows.name:
You are just leading people into disaster
for your own amusement!

rows.label: qst200231_0200
rows.name:
Heh! All I ever did was to
give them a gentle nudge...

rows.label: qst200231_0210
rows.name:
I am done talkin' with ya.
It's time to put 'em up!

rows.label: qst200231_0220
rows.name:
Gird your loins for a nice big taste of
steaming justice!
